ribute to the eclipse of an optically thick region\nat the centre of the disc. This model could also account for the behaviour of\nother SW Sex stars where the Balmer lines show only a shallow eclipse compared\nto the continuum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Jun 2004 22:49:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
